  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective randomized clinical trial to assess the effect of in-hospital intensive
      counseling and follow-up vs. usual care, on re-admission rates of patients with Asthma.

      The study population will include asthma patients admitted to internal Medicine departments
      and medical ICU at Soroka University Medical Center, due to asthma exacerbation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
